tyle=\"font-size: 13px; color: #999; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;\">You have <strong style=\"color: #fff;\">90 minutes</strong> to complete your analysis once you start. This simulates real deal room time pressure. Make sure you have uninterrupted time before clicking.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #222; text-align: center;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #444; margin: 0;\">FinApply.ai · Founding Cohort · Batch 1</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
